---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sustainability & ESG" description="Our commitment to environmental stewardship, community empowerment, ethical governance, and cultural preservation in Bali.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-125 flex items-center justify-center bg-stone-900 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-stone-900/60 via-stone-900/40 to-stone-900/80 z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501785888041-af3ef285b470?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="hero-animate text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Our Commitment</p>
      <h1 class="hero-animate hero-animate-delay-1 font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-stone-50 leading-tight">
        Luxury That<br/>Gives Back
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Our Philosophy</p>
      <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
      
      <div class="prose-luxury text-center">
        <p>
          We believe that true luxury cannot exist at the expense of others—not 
          the communities who call Bali home, not the ecosystems that make it 
          sacred, not the traditions that give it soul. Our commitment to 
          sustainability is not a marketing position. It is the foundation 
          upon which every journey is built.
        </p>
        <p>
          When you travel with Bali Encore, you become part of a circle of 
          reciprocity. The island gives to you—its beauty, its wisdom, its 
          transformative power. And through us, you give back—supporting the 
          people, places, and practices that make Bali extraordinary.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Environmental Commitment -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-125">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518495973542-4542c06a5843?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Environment</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900 mb-6">
            Guardians of the Sacred Land
          </h2>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Bali's landscapes are not merely beautiful—they are sacred. The 
              rice terraces, the volcanic peaks, the coral reefs, the ancient 
              forests—each is a living temple that demands our reverence and 
              protection.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Carbon Consciousness:</strong> We 
                  calculate and offset the carbon footprint of every journey, 
                  investing in verified reforestation and renewable energy 
                  projects within Bali.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Eco-Conscious Partners:</strong> We 
                  work exclusively with accommodations and experiences that 
                  demonstrate genuine environmental commitment—not greenwashing, 
                  but measurable action.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Conservation Support:</strong> A 
                  portion of every journey directly funds Bali's conservation 
                  efforts—protecting endangered species, preserving marine 
                  ecosystems, and restoring degraded lands.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Plastic-Free Commitment:</strong> We 
                  have eliminated single-use plastics from every aspect of our 
                  operations and encourage our partners to do the same.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community Impact -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Social</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900 mb-6">
            Empowering Communities
          </h2>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              The Balinese people are not service providers—they are the soul 
              of every journey we create. Their knowledge, their traditions, 
              their hospitality are gifts that deserve fair recognition and 
              genuine partnership.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Fair Compensation:</strong> We pay 
                  above-market rates to all local partners, guides, artisans, 
                  and communities. Excellence deserves recognition.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Local Ownership:</strong> We 
                  prioritize partnerships with Balinese-owned businesses, 
                  ensuring that tourism wealth stays within the community.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Education Support:</strong> We 
                  contribute to educational initiatives that help young 
                  Balinese develop skills while maintaining connection to 
                  their cultural heritage.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Village Development:</strong> A 
                  portion of every journey supports infrastructure and 
                  development projects in rural Balinese communities.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative h-125 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604999333679-b86d54738315?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cultural Preservation -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-900 text-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-125">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555400038-63f5ba517a47?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <p class="text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Culture</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-50 mb-6">
            Honoring Living Traditions
          </h2>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Bali's cultural traditions are not attractions to be consumed—they 
              are living treasures that have been passed down through generations 
              and must be passed on to generations yet to come.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-50">Respectful Engagement:</strong> We 
                  ensure that every cultural experience is conducted with 
                  appropriate reverence, following protocols established by 
                  community elders.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-50">Artisan Support:</strong> We 
                  connect travelers with master artisans in ways that provide 
                  meaningful income while honoring the integrity of traditional 
                  crafts.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-50">Sacred Space Protection:</strong> We 
                  never treat temples or ceremonies as photo opportunities. 
                  Access to sacred spaces is earned through proper preparation 
                  and genuine intention.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-50">Heritage Preservation:</strong> We 
                  support initiatives that document and preserve Balinese 
                  cultural knowledge for future generations.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ethical Governance -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Governance</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900 mb-6">
            Integrity in Everything
          </h2>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Our commitment to ethical practice extends beyond environmental 
              and social responsibility to encompass every aspect of how we 
              operate. Transparency, accountability, and integrity are not 
              aspirations—they are requirements.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Transparent Pricing:</strong> We 
                  are clear about where your investment goes. No hidden fees, 
                  no obscured margins, no exploitation of information asymmetry.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Partner Vetting:</strong> Every 
                  partner in our network is carefully vetted for ethical 
                  practice, environmental responsibility, and fair treatment 
                  of workers.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Continuous Improvement:</strong> We 
                  regularly audit our practices and those of our partners, 
                  always seeking ways to deepen our positive impact.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
                <p>
                  <strong class="text-stone-900">Honest Communication:</strong> We 
                  tell you the truth—about what is possible, what is 
                  appropriate, and what serves your journey best.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative h-125 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Carbon Consciousness -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Carbon Consciousness</p>
      <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-12">
        Travel That Heals
      </h2>
      
      <div class="prose-luxury text-center">
        <p>
          We acknowledge the environmental cost of travel. Every flight, every 
          transfer, every experience has a carbon footprint. Rather than ignore 
          this reality, we address it directly.
        </p>
        <p>
          For every journey we create, we calculate the total carbon impact and 
          invest in verified offset projects—not distant abstractions, but local 
          initiatives that benefit Bali directly. Reforestation of degraded 
          lands. Support for renewable energy adoption in rural communities. 
          Protection of carbon-sequestering ecosystems.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our goal is not carbon neutrality—it is carbon positivity. We aim for 
          every journey to leave Bali better than it found it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518495973542-4542c06a5843?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stone-900/70"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-8">
        Journey with Purpose
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        When you travel with us, your transformation becomes part of 
        Bali's flourishing.
      </p>
      <a href="/begin" class="btn-luxury-outline">Begin Your Journey</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
